ComicInfo.Summary: The End of the End (or Happy Entrails To You...): T-Ray's real name is Wade Wilson and Deadpool is the violent monster who killed his wife. With this mind bending, origin shattering revelation on the table, Deadpool shrugs it off and battles T-Ray and Mercedes anyway. With the fight ending inconclusively, Deadpool is then forced to refight all of the people he has taken down in his long and violent life. He is 99% killed and has a reunion with his old flame, Death.
